News.Title: DU Digital Global Wins Bid for Embassy of India Seoul Project
News.Summary: DU Digital Global has been declared the L1 (lowest) bidder for a Request for Proposal (RFP) issued by the Embassy of India in Seoul. This suggests that the company has submitted the most competitive bid for a project or service required by the Indian Embassy in South Korea.
